title: 112: Preseason Preview
itunes:title: 112: Preseason Preview
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the opening week of preseason games. Then the guys debate if Jacksonville defensive lineman Dante Fowler and Chicago wide receiver Kevin White can bounce back in a big way for 2016.
